track_notes: Linear walk route on tracks - very easy walking with little ascent. Caught the L2 bus (€2.55 per person)from La Savina (the port) up to El Pilar. Walked over the hill and did the activation and then walked down to Es Calo where we hailed a passing taxi back to the port. (€18.5+tip) see my blog for more details (when I write the trip up)
track_title: Torre Mola using public transport and taxi back to the Port
